84
00:05:35,270 --> 00:05:36,600
Though you look different,

85
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:39,160
I can still sense

86
00:05:39,310 --> 00:05:40,680
that familiar scent and expression

87
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:42,160
on you.

88
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:47,800
