95
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:05,040
My father brought me to Moonlight Heights to borrow the Chaos Pearl.

96
00:06:07,310 --> 00:06:08,780
Everyone looked at me

97
00:06:08,870 --> 00:06:10,120
